9.1 The Licensor is not responsible for damages, loss of revenue, corruption of data, or issues resulting from use of the Tools.
9.2 The Licensee assumes all risks associated with using the Tools.

LIMITATION OF LIABILITY AND INDEMNIFICATION
10.0 In no event shall the Licensor be liable for any claim exceeding the amount paid by the Licensee for Excess Revenue obligations, if any.
10.1 This limitation applies to negligence, contract disputes, or tort claims.
10.2 Indemnification: The Licensee agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the Licensor (SourBit Studio) from any claims, lawsuits, liabilities, damages, or penalties arising out of the Licenseeâ€™s use of the Tools or the operation of their Projects. The Licensor cannot be held liable for any legal violations, copyright infringements, or unlawful acts committed by the Licensee or their Projects.

EXPORT CONTROL AND SANCTIONS
11.0 The Licensee may not use, export, re-export, or transfer the Tools or Projects created with the Tools to any country, entity, or person subject to sanctions or embargoes imposed by the European Union (EU), the United Nations (UN), or the United States of America (USA).
11.1 The Licensee represents and warrants that they are not a citizen of, or located within, an embargoed or sanctioned nation and are not prohibited from receiving the Tools under applicable export control laws.
11.2 Creating Projects that violate international export laws or facilitate illegal activities is strictly prohibited.

